{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"6f1701cc9a","title":"刘少奇对全国妇联党组同志谈话记录","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"fa838aa620","index":0,"year":1958,"month":6,"day":14,"articleId":"6f1701cc9a"}],"tags":[{"id":"314ad57c4d","name":"对话","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"7aac50a8c5","name":"文艺战线","type":"主题/事件"},{"id":"e759231f2d","name":"农业战线","type":"主题/事件"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-dayuejin","name":"中国大跃进-大饥荒数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"2f412bb744","name":"郭沫若"}]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-dayuejin":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"606e06ced6","type":"title","text":"《大跃进之歌》序","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"6f1701cc9a"},{"id":"0fd5f6d1e2","type":"authors","text":"郭沫若","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"6f1701cc9a"},{"id":"41ceda4c68","type":"paragraph","text":"这部《大跃进之歌》我在清样中先读了一遍，受到了很大的鼓舞。这表示着目前工农业生产的大跃进，也表示着诗歌生产的大跃进。","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"6f1701cc9a"},{"id":"4ae716052e","type":"paragraph","text":"目前的中国真正是诗歌的汪洋大海，诗歌的新宇宙。六亿人民仿佛都是诗人，创造力的大解放就象火山爆发一样，气势磅礴，空前未有。","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"6f1701cc9a"},{"id":"06e32b6559","type":"paragraph","text":"请看这几首绝妙的歌辞吧。","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"6f1701cc9a"},{"id":"41d421685c","type":"paragraph","text":"一挑鸳篼不多大，","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"6f1701cc9a"},{"id":"e97f70f320","type":"paragraph","text":"修塘开堰挑泥巴。","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"6f1701cc9a"},{"id":"df106dd0a2","type":"paragraph","text":"莫嫌我的鸳篼小，","index":7,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"6f1701cc9a"},{"id":"63a9add854","type":"paragraph","text":"两匹大山装得下。","index":8,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"6f1701cc9a"},{"id":"f7bfe437f0","type":"paragraph","text":" ——《四川新山歌》","index":9,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"6f1701cc9a"},{"id":"7cb677f68f","type":"paragraph","text":"箢头装得满满，","index":10,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"6f1701cc9a"},{"id":"492ac6a76b","type":"paragraph","text":"扁担压得弯弯，","index":11,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"6f1701cc9a"},{"id":"e88d0bc3a6","type":"paragraph","text":"孩子的妈妈呀，你看看；","index":12,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"6f1701cc9a"},{"id":"2e538c8f67","type":"paragraph","text":"我一头挑着一座山。","index":13,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"6f1701cc9a"},{"id":"41b65c1c52","type":"paragraph","text":"——《湖北麻城新歌谣》","index":14,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"6f1701cc9a"},{"id":"fa009f7acb","type":"paragraph","text":"提起旱田变水田，","index":15,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"6f1701cc9a"},{"id":"f7416ef603","type":"paragraph","text":"一担子能担两架山。","index":16,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"6f1701cc9a"},{"id":"77ce119043","type":"paragraph","text":"提起农业大跃进，","index":17,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"6f1701cc9a"},{"id":"bbd20671d6","type":"paragraph","text":"日头都能够摘下天。","index":18,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"6f1701cc9a"},{"id":"9500891660","type":"paragraph","text":"提起前头的好日子，","index":19,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"6f1701cc9a"},{"id":"ae7db74464","type":"paragraph","text":"肚子变成了蜂糖罐。","index":20,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"6f1701cc9a"},{"id":"bcafbc4db2","type":"paragraph","text":" ——《伏牛山新歌谣》","index":21,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"6f1701cc9a"},{"id":"ec4f74c0e5","type":"paragraph","text":"这是多么现实，多么豪迈，多么形象化！地不分东西南北，着想差不多是相同的，这儿有着情感上的共鸣。五月尾上我到河北省涿鹿县去看那儿进行的“劈山大渠”工程，在工程地段的快报上也看到了这样一首歌谣：","index":22,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"6f1701cc9a"},{"id":"cc04c65a7b","type":"paragraph","text":"扁担不长七尺三，","index":23,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"6f1701cc9a"},{"id":"945cf72434","type":"paragraph","text":"箩筐不大柳条编，","index":24,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"6f1701cc9a"},{"id":"020d26fa6f","type":"paragraph","text":"你甭小视这玩艺，","index":25,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"6f1701cc9a"},{"id":"cf381aacee","type":"paragraph","text":"昨天担走两座山。","index":26,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"6f1701cc9a"},{"id":"c4be962647","type":"paragraph","text":"最后一句简直令人拍案惊奇。我们要说这些歌谣是革命的浪漫主义与革命的现实主义的结合，我看是一点也不夸大的。诗人们应当从这儿学习。","index":27,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"6f1701cc9a"},{"id":"96fd0eca1b","type":"paragraph","text":"这个集子里面有工人农民的歌谣，也有专业作者的诗篇。两者比较起来，工人、农民的歌谣更有生气，更有振动人心的韵律。可见诗歌也和一切物质生产的成品一样，应该从劳动生产中产生出来。从这里便可以体会到下放政策的重要性。集子中已有一些歌咏下放干部的作品。这些干部同志经过劳动锻炼的结果，由下马而扎根，由观花而开花，可以断言，中国的文艺作品必会有在质、量双方都有所提高的大规模的丰收。","index":28,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"6f1701cc9a"},{"id":"c5518bfda9","type":"paragraph","text":"文艺的韵律是和劳动生产分不开来的。从来的民歌民谣主要表现着农业生产的旋律，今天的大跃进之歌绝大部分也产生自农村，思想内容已有极大的跃进，但在形式和韵律上的变化不很大，基本上还是七言诗的调子。随着农业的机械化，农村的电气化，我相信将来的歌谣形式可能会发生较大的变革。这个倾向在工人所作的诗歌中已可以看出一点前兆。","index":29,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"6f1701cc9a"},{"id":"bf5c42ee0f","type":"paragraph","text":"花炮为矿山的春天开道，","index":30,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"6f1701cc9a"},{"id":"da2c990573","type":"paragraph","text":"五彩纸好象鲜花满地，","index":31,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"6f1701cc9a"},{"id":"c7c027732c","type":"paragraph","text":"决心书，保证书，挑战节……","index":32,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"6f1701cc9a"},{"id":"2243293adc","type":"paragraph","text":"一摆摆了好几里！","index":33,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"6f1701cc9a"},{"id":"9521b31627","type":"paragraph","text":" ——孙友田《矿山跨上千里马》","index":34,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"6f1701cc9a"},{"id":"e384baba25","type":"paragraph","text":"赶吧，赶吧，快马加鞭！","index":35,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"6f1701cc9a"},{"id":"96bad061a7","type":"paragraph","text":"让我们的轮胎赶上英国的“邓禄普”","index":36,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"6f1701cc9a"},{"id":"608f10ecfe","type":"paragraph","text":"需要多少时间？","index":37,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"6f1701cc9a"},{"id":"40d593dbd9","type":"paragraph","text":"厂长：“决不会超出四年！”","index":38,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"6f1701cc9a"},{"id":"ffcaecb7ff","type":"paragraph","text":"工程师：“不，只需要三年半！”","index":39,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"6f1701cc9a"},{"id":"ef9e16188d","type":"paragraph","text":"工人：“我们坚决保证三年！”","index":40,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"6f1701cc9a"},{"id":"f131974509","type":"paragraph","text":" ——沈国梁《在跃进会上》","index":41,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"6f1701cc9a"},{"id":"311d5b0b58","type":"paragraph","text":"有的朋友或许会说这不是歌谣体，但我的看法是：这可能是歌谣的一种新形式，是以既成的歌谣体和旧诗词为基础的一种发展。","index":42,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"6f1701cc9a"},{"id":"176adfca06","type":"paragraph","text":"月下挖泥河，千担万担，","index":43,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"6f1701cc9a"},{"id":"4e86ba3cb8","type":"paragraph","text":"扁担儿——月牙弯弯，","index":44,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"6f1701cc9a"},{"id":"bfd74b312a","type":"paragraph","text":"咕，咕，象飞着一群大雁。","index":45,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"6f1701cc9a"},{"id":"1f107c4ced","type":"paragraph","text":"北风呼啸，汗珠满脸，","index":46,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"6f1701cc9a"},{"id":"4a4132ed89","type":"paragraph","text":"今年多施河泥千斤，","index":47,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"6f1701cc9a"},{"id":"0a212a644e","type":"paragraph","text":"明年增产食粮万担","index":48,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"6f1701cc9a"},{"id":"a47e44be27","type":"paragraph","text":" ——李苏卿《月下挖泥河》","index":49,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"6f1701cc9a"},{"id":"4ec22e0eb6","type":"paragraph","text":"这却是从农村里产生出来的歌，而韵律也差不多摆脱了固定的形式，更加生动活泼了。","index":50,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"6f1701cc9a"},{"id":"d0d1271a1e","type":"paragraph","text":"在这里似乎显示着新诗歌的一个方向。","index":51,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"6f1701cc9a"},{"id":"c397fc713e","type":"paragraph","text":" 一九五八年六月十六日","index":52,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"6f1701cc9a"},{"id":"e56b89762e","type":"paragraph","text":" 来源：选自1958年《诗刊》第7期。","index":53,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"6f1701cc9a"}],"page":{"id":"0767e4528a","publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"6f1701cc9a","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}